Template: permafrost-vault/port
Type: string
Default: 3100
Description: Backend port for PERMAFROST Vault:
 The port the backend server will listen on. The relay will use
 the next port (e.g., 3101). Choose a port that is not in use.

Template: permafrost-vault/domain
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Domain name for PERMAFROST Vault:
 Used in the nginx server_name directive and for generating
 session join URLs. Use 'localhost' for local-only access.
